**\n\nI'm now focusing on specific component structures. Each resource subpage will use the standard inner page width. I'm planning for distinctive headers, category systems, and modules. I'll include breadcrumbs, related links, and a Premium CTA on each. I will also be focused on adding specific interaction patterns for each subpage.\n\nI'm now defining the mobile strategy as well, with responsive grid layouts. Compact navigation and readable typographic sizing are also key. I'll focus on creating the individual page files, starting with `/resources/blog/page.tsx` and working my way down.\n\n\n"}}
